data.clean_description: 10 POT. Brownies. Made fresh with each order. be great to help sleeping I think , or just to chill out and enjoy life. These are mini-muffin brownies , each one is a couple bites. They have a mild cannabis taste , but I think it s minimal. If you have a high tolerance eat two or three at once. Most people will feel a nice high from one. 1000 mg thc total 100 mg each brownie.
data.name: 10 POT Brownies Made fresh
